import Vue from 'vue'
import axios from 'axios'
// import VueAxios from 'vue-axios'
import App from './App.vue'
import '@/assets/css/tailwind.css'
import 'remixicon/fonts/remixicon.css'
import Router from '@/router'

Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router: Router,
  axios,
  render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app')
